{"tid":2149300,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"1999年, 有個報販唔肯買東方日報, 之後俾人斬死咗","createTime":"2020-08-10T10:28:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T03:25:01.000Z","uid":51963,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"18e68061ed091949a386fc512b1b25d578f0e63f","tid":2149300,"uid":51963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T10:28:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%A0%B1%E8%B2%A9%E9%9C%9E%E5%A7%90%E8%A2%AB%E6%AE%BA%E6%A1%88\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E8%25B2%25A9%25E9%259C%259E%25E5%25A7%2590%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E6%25A1%2588&d=6XXjbPj9602%2BpZUfgYO1mEbB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=5b111245\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%A0%B1%E8%B2%A9%E9%9C%9E%E5%A7%90%E8%A2%AB%E6%AE%BA%E6%A1%88</a><br />\n<br />\n話說東方日報既發行商青匯要深水埗報販買多D佢既報紙<br />\n(類似我搬盤桔入你鋪頭, 你就一定要買啦, 唔買後果自負)<br />\n報販霞姐就代表同區其他報販拒絕, 點知幾日後就直接俾人斬死咗<br />\n係呀, 有個報販唔買東方日報之後就俾人斬死了<br />\n最吊詭係: 在2007年3月27日，多份報章都以頭版大篇幅報道判刑的消息，不過，<strong>東方日報</strong>和<strong>太陽報</strong>則完全沒有報道此新聞。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過, 今日東方日報仲係好地地呀"},{"pid":"61ac9cf37fbe044ffdc1a73fc8af7844af89ce44","tid":2149300,"uid":288304,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T10:29:17.000Z","msg":"聽日邊個賣蘋果..."},{"pid":"0b3306c586117c80bdfbd9c9698e83bfcb2fc1e6","tid":2149300,"uid":301495,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T10:32:16.000Z","msg":"呢單野當年好轟動嫁<br />\n東方靠咩起家大家知啦<br />\n咩背景咪用返一貫手段對付人<br />\n可憐個霞姐"},{"pid":"0aa2c8f2bb4a29beaaaa7a5617265ae61a03c3ae","tid":2149300,"uid":301666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T10:32:56.000Z","msg":"每日賣一百份嘅報紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25a944ab528818e9486d114460796508e8fbd904","tid":2149300,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0aa2c8f2bb4a29beaaaa7a5617265